   <section name="Classpath Directive">

    <subsection name="Description">
<p>A classpath directive qualifies the defintion of the enclosing classloader. The enclosing classloader shall be established with the jar resources declared within the classpath.  The resulting classloader shall be made available to the enclosing container and subsidiary components (including subsidiary containers). An example of a classpath declaration is included below.</p>
    </subsection>

     <subsection name="Nested Elements">
        <table>
          <tr><th>Element</th><th>Occurance</th><th>Description</th></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><a href="artifact.html">artifact</a></td><td>n</td>
            <td>
             An artifact directive.
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><a href="fileset/index.html">fileset</a></td><td>n</td>
            <td>
             A fileset directive.
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
    </subsection>

    <subsection name="Sample XML (using artifacts)">
<source>
&lt;classpath&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/logging/dpml-logging-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/context/dpml-context-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/configuration/dpml-configuration-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/service/dpml-service-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/activity/dpml-activity-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/composition/dpml-classic-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/transit/dpml-transit-main#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/meta/dpml-meta-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/parameters/dpml-parameters-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/util/dpml-util-i18n#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/extension/dpml-extension-api#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/context/dpml-context-impl#316</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
  &lt;artifact&gt;<font color="darkred">jar:dpml/test/dpml-test-playground</font>&lt;/artifact&gt;
&lt;/classpath&gt;
</source>
    </subsection>

    <subsection name="Sample XML (using filesets)">
<source>
&lt;classpath&gt;
  &lt;fileset dir="<font color="darkred">lib</font>"&gt;
    &lt;include name="<font color="darkred">dpml-service-api-316.jar</font>"/&gt;
    &lt;include name="<font color="darkred">dpml-logging-api-316.jar</font>"/&gt;
  &lt;/fileset&gt;
&lt;/classpath&gt;
</source>
    </subsection>

    </section>
